NAME: TREFOIL TEE
DESCRIPTION: The adidas Trefoil first appeared on the scene in 1972, and it continues to make its mark. This archive-inspired t-shirt celebrates the symbol's legacy. It's made of cotton jersey for a soft feel.

NAME: 3-STRIPES CLUB POLO SHIRT
DESCRIPTION: Stay cool on court when your opponent turns up the heat. This tennis polo shirt keeps you comfortable with ventilated mesh panels on the back and under the arms. The underarm gussets give you space to swing, so you can unleash your entire range of shots. This polo is made of comfortable doubleknit fabric.
